trans-unit.source: Provides common functionality across communication protocols for creating <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription"></xref> objects from classes that are identified as Web services.
trans-unit.target: Gir felles funksjonalitet på tvers av kommunikasjonsprotokoller for oppretting av <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription"> </xref> objekter fra klasser som er identifisert som Web services.

trans-unit.source: The abstract ProtocolReflector class and its concrete derived classes create <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription> objects from classes that are identified as Web services with the <xref:System.Web.Services.WebServiceAttribute> attribute.
trans-unit.target: Abstrakt ProtocolReflector klassen og tilhørende konkrete avledede klasser opprette <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription>objekter fra klasser som er identifisert som webtjenester ved hjelp av <xref:System.Web.Services.WebServiceAttribute>attributtet.</xref:System.Web.Services.WebServiceAttribute> </xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription>

trans-unit.source: Each concrete ProtocolReflector-derived class generates <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription> objects according to a specified communication protocol; ProtocolReflector provides common functionality regardless of the protocol.
trans-unit.target: Hver konkrete avledede ProtocolReflector klasse genererer <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription>objekter i henhold til en angitt kommunikasjonsprotokollen. ProtocolReflector gir felles funksjonalitet uavhengig protokollen.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription>

trans-unit.source: An output <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription> instance can be used to generate a Web Services Description Language (WSDL) document with the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription.Write%2A> method or one of the available overloads.
trans-unit.target: En output <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription>forekomsten kan brukes til å generere et Web Services beskrivelse språket (WSDL)-dokument med den <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription.Write%2A>metoden eller en tilgjengelig overlastingene.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription.Write%2A> </xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription> instance can also be used by the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter> class and related classes to generate client proxy code or abstract server code.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription>forekomsten kan også brukes av den <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter>klassen og relaterte klassene til å generere klienten proxy code abstrakt server kode.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter> </xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription>

trans-unit.source: The ProtocolReflector class uses the <xref:System.Web.Services.WebServiceBindingAttribute> to create a <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription> for each binding it identifies in the Web service class.
trans-unit.target: Klassen ProtocolReflector bruker til <xref:System.Web.Services.WebServiceBindingAttribute>å opprette en <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription>for hver binding identifiserer i Web service klassen.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription> </xref:System.Web.Services.WebServiceBindingAttribute>

trans-unit.source: If that attribute is not present, the ProtocolReflector class creates a single binding for the entire class.
trans-unit.target: Hvis attributtet ikke finnes, oppretter klassen ProtocolReflector en enkelt binding for hele klassen.

trans-unit.source: For each Web service method (a method in the Web service class appearing with the <xref:System.Web.Services.WebMethodAttribute>) belonging to a binding, a class derived from ProtocolReflector generates an operation and associated messages that are added to the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription> object.
trans-unit.target: Tjeneste metoden for hver webprogrammer (en metode i Web serviceklassen vises med den <xref:System.Web.Services.WebMethodAttribute>) som hører til en binding genererer en klasse som er avledet fra ProtocolReflector en operasjon og tilknyttede meldinger som er lagt til i <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription>objektet.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription> </xref:System.Web.Services.WebMethodAttribute>

trans-unit.source: Typically, a developer uses these classes indirectly through the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionReflector> class, instead of directly invoking classes derived from ProtocolReflector.
trans-unit.target: Vanligvis en utvikler bruker disse klassene indirekte til den <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionReflector>klasse, i stedet for å aktivere direkte klasser som er avledet fra ProtocolReflector.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionReflector>
